Table 5. We com-
pared our results with the original methods that we adopt in our architecture. 
Our model with both ResNet-50 and ResNet-101 backends outperformed the 
original implementations. This is not a surprising result since our network is 
only dealing with a single class whereas the original implementations handle 80 
object classes.
